Class EstateSquare

java.lang.Object
Square
EstateSquare
public class EstateSquare
extends Square
EstateSquare is a subclass of Square, representing a square within an Estate. They have different properties based on which part of the Estate they are: (inside, outside, corner, entrance).
Author:
johnh
